        "body": "The purpose of this commit is to avoid potential problems associated with BOMs, since they have been known to halt some script interpreters and compilers in their tracks.\r\n\r\nPersonally speaking, I have never experienced any problems by omitting the BOM.  But I write/code primarily in English.  If non-English writing/coding doesn't necessitate a BOM then it seems that the appropriate option would be to forgo its use, by default.",
