        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "It's not the goal of the Java Style Guide to address all possible configuration issues; we require Java source code to be UTF-8 for numerous reasons, but the presence or absence of a BOM is not something we need to make a ruling on. Leave it off when possible, as the UTF-8 spec already says.",
